Badrinath ki Dulhaniya: Alia Bhatt makes Varun Bhatt solve math sums for promotions 
3-3-2017 
Bollywood actors Alia Bhatt and Varun Dhawan are painting the town red with their promotional antics for their upcoming film, Badrinath ki Dulhania.

Alia Bhatt and Varun Dhawan made their Bollywood debut with Student of the Year.

Alia and Varun have shared a video on their Instagram that shows Vaidehi (Alia) asking Badri (Varun) to solve some math calculations. The calculations are rather easy: Subtract 5 from 12, add three and then subtract two. Varun stumbles a bit, but gets the answer right.

Read more

The catch is, the answer is the number days left for the release of Badrinath ki Dulhaniya - eight.

8 Days To Go!!!!!!! #badrinathkidulhania @varundvn A post shared by Alia ✨⭐️ (@aliaabhatt) on Mar 2, 2017 at 12:25am PST

Badrinath Ki Dulhania is a spin-off of its prequel Humpty Sharma Ki Dulhania, which released in 2014. The film, which reprises its star cast, marks the third film of Alia and Varun together. They made their Bollywood debut with Student of the Year (2012).

